import React, { useContext } from "react"; import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; import { LanguageContext } from "chemin/vers/LanguageContext"; import { translations } from "chemin/vers/les-traductions"; export default function Register() { const { lang } = useContext(LanguageContext); const t = translations[lang]; return ( <>
{t.title}
{t.forgetPassword}
{t.login}
); }
